@startuml
title 图3-2 系统数据流与控制流示意图

top to bottom direction
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam roundcorner 0

rectangle "环境数据" as Data
rectangle "设备端" as Device
rectangle "边缘端" as Edge
rectangle "Web端" as Web
rectangle "执行模块" as Actuator
actor 用户

Data --> Device 
Device --> Edge 
Edge --> Web 

用户 ..> Web 
Web ..> Edge 
Edge ..> Actuator 

legend right
实线：数据流
虚线：控制流
endlegend

@enduml